      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p>The workspace editor allows you to control the various aspects of asset management for RenderMan for Blender. <br/><br/>To open the editor, go to the output properties and click Open Workspace.</p><p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637132/RenderManForBlender_outputicon.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432686861&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637132/RenderManForBlender_outputicon.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432686861&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637156\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManForBlender_outputicon.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637132\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"d6f9b97d-630b-449b-b4c4-de1b9dde1542\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span></p><p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637132/RenderManForBlender_workspace.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432686861&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637132/RenderManForBlender_workspace.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432686861&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637159\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManForBlender_workspace.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637132\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"153dd88d-2d87-4138-ab2a-c610e771b4d6\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span></p><p><br/>A new window should open that looks similar to the image below</p><p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637132/RenderManForBlender_workspace_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432687038&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/544637132/RenderManForBlender_workspace_1.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754432687038&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"544637162\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderManForBlender_workspace_1.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"544637132\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"3a24f40f-f7dc-4eed-b682-72f9fb200dec\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span><br/><br/></p><hr/><h3 id=\"WorkspaceinBlender-OutputPath\">Output Path</h3><p>The root output path for all generated files for the scene. Can be referenced with the &lt;OUT&gt; token in other paths.</p><h3 id=\"WorkspaceinBlender-RIBOutputPath\">RIB Output Path</h3><p>Controls the output path and naming of RIB files.</p><h3 id=\"WorkspaceinBlender-BeautyImageOutputPath\">Beauty Image Output Path</h3><p>Controls the output path and naming of the beauty image.</p><h3 id=\"WorkspaceinBlender-AOVImageOutputPath\">AOV Image Output Path</h3><p>Controls the output path and naming of the secondary AOV images.</p><h3 id=\"WorkspaceinBlender-Bake3DIlluminationOutputPath\">Bake 3D Illumination Output Path</h3><p>Controls the output path and naming of the pointcloud files when doing 3D illumination baking.</p><h3 id=\"WorkspaceinBlender-Bake2DIlluminationOutputPath\">Bake 2D Illumination Output Path</h3><p>Controls the output path and naming of 2D texture files when doing 2D illumination baking.</p><h3 id=\"WorkspaceinBlender-VersionandTake\">Version and Take</h3><p>These control the values of the &lt;version&gt; and &lt;take&gt; tokens.</p><h3 id=\"WorkspaceinBlender-UserTokens\">User Tokens</h3><p>This section allows you to add your own token/value pairs that use the output paths above or in various file path and string settings. <br/>These user tokens are saved as part of the scene.<br/><br/><br/></p>"
    }
  },
